# IconControl

Icon controls allow users to perform an action or mark a selection and are used for similar, task-based options within a workflow.
They are ideal for interfaces where buttons aren’t meant to draw a lot of attention.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/icon-control
```

```tsx
import { IconControl } from '@ids-ts/icon-control';
```

## Props API

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `children` | `ReactNode` | No | The icon to display |
| `className` | `string` | No | Custom className for additional css to be applied to component |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | No | Prop to render the control as disabled |
| `label` | `string` | No | Prop to add label to icon control |
| `labelAlignment` | `'left' | 'right'` | No | Prop to align label |
| `onClick` | `MouseEventHandler<HTMLButtonElement>` | No | Callback handler function that is fired when a Checkbox has been clicked. |
| `onKeyDown` | `KeyboardEventHandler` | No | Keydown event handler prop for icon control |
| `onMouseDown` | `MouseEventHandler` | No | Mouse event handler prop for icon control |
| `selected` | `boolean` | No | Prop to set icon control as selected. Helpful when using icon-controls with fly-outs. |
| `complementary` | `boolean` | No | Prop to set icon control to use complementary colors. Helpful when displaying on a dark colored background. |
| `shape` | `Shapes` | No | Prop to change the shape of the button. Currently supports square and circle. If circle is selected, using a label is not supported. |
| `size` | `Sizes` | No | - |

<details>
<summary>Full TypeScript Interface</summary>

```typescript
export interface IconControlProps extends ThemeableElement<'button'> {
  /** Aria label */
  'aria-label'?: string;
  /** The icon to display */
  children?: ReactNode;
  /** Custom className for additional css to be applied to component */
  className?: string;
  /** Prop to render the control as disabled */
  disabled?: boolean;
  /** Prop to add label to icon control */
  label?: string;
  /** Prop to align label */
  labelAlignment?: 'left' | 'right';
  /** Callback handler function that is fired when a Checkbox has been clicked. */
  onClick?: MouseEventHandler<HTMLButtonElement>;
  /** Keydown event handler prop for icon control */
  onKeyDown?: KeyboardEventHandler;
  /** Mouse event handler prop for icon control */
  onMouseDown?: MouseEventHandler;
  /** Prop to set icon control as selected. Helpful when using icon-controls with fly-outs. */
  selected?: boolean;
  /** Prop to set icon control to use complementary colors. Helpful when displaying on a dark colored background. */
  complementary?: boolean;
  /** Prop to change the shape of the button. Currently supports square and circle. If circle is selected, using a label is not supported. */
  shape?: Shapes;
  /**
   * IconControl button size - one of x-small, small, medium, large
   *
   * @default 'small'
   */
  size?: Sizes;
}

export type Shapes = 'square' | 'circle';

export type Sizes = 'x-small' | 'small' | 'medium' | 'large';
```

</details>

